data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLERS! Completely updated! Brand New Roof, HVAC system, Siding, Shutters, Windows, Doors, Flooring, Paint, Fireplace, Bathroom, Kitchen, and More! This 3 bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is absolutely a must see. It's like a little hidden gem, up on the hill. A beautifully landscaped front area makes its way to the front porch that is perfect for a swing to overlook the nature beauty of across the street. It will make you feel like you are in a treehouse. Open the front door and find the open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining. A gorgeous fireplace is the perfect central area in the living space flanked by the oversized island found in the kitchen. Brand new granite countertops and cabinetry make up this stately kitchen. The kitchen features an oversized breakfast area that is perfect for any dining room table. The laundry area is deep enough for extra storage or as a utility closet. The hallway bathroom has been 100% updated with tile, immaculate vanity area with double sinks and mirrors and a stand-up shower built for a king or queen alike. All three bedrooms feature the same vinyl hardwood flooring featured throughout the rest of the home. A new deck awaits out back for a private oasis. Both storage buildings on the property convey. Do not miss your opportunity to own this Greenville secret!
